overview:
The quick story is Electcollect is short for Electric Collection, because without modern day electricity you wouldn’t be able to collect this unique audio and visual mobile content.

Electcollect.com specializes in bringing you 24,000 custom and unique original ringtones and 20,000 art-tones for your cell phone. We are continuously updating our website with new ringtones and art-tones so you can always have todays newest visual and audio content for your cell phone. Personalize your cell phone with ringtones and art-tones and join the community of Electcollect.com members are defining the way cell phones ring.

Our art-tones allow you to add a little spice to the look of your color screen phone. We have many art-tones to choose from ranging from beautiful sunset images to abstract digital fine art images.

Electcollect.com lets you save money buy emailing you content to your email address and giving you directions on how to upload to save yourself money in this economy. Electcollect is the most unique and cost effective ringtone/art-tone company in the industry.

Electcollect.com is owned and operated by Wallestate LLC., and pays all appropriate royalties to artists through mechanical licensing agreements with publishers and performance licensing agreements.
